\[
\begin{aligned}f_{0} & =1\\
f_{2k+2} & =\frac{(2k+2)(2k+1)-(l+1)l}{(2k+3)(2k+2)}f_{2k}\qquad k=0,1,2,\dots
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

于是方程的解可以表示为
