status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[Wronskian]
\end_layout

\end_inset

对于 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 个至少 
\begin_inset Formula $(n-1)$
\end_inset

 阶可导的函数 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ u_{i}(x)\right\} _{i=1}^{n}$
\end_inset

，称
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W(x;u_{1},\dots,u_{n})\equiv W_{12\cdots n}(x)\coloneqq\begin{vmatrix}\begin{array}{llll}
u_{1} & u_{2} & \cdots & u_{n}\\
u_{1}' & u_{2}' & \cdots & u_{n}'\\
\cdots & \cdots & \cdots & \cdots\\
u_{1}^{(n-1)} & u_{2}^{(n-1)} & \cdots & u_{n}^{(n-1)}
\end{array}\end{vmatrix}
\]

\end_inset

为它们的“Wronskian（行列式）”。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
对于 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 个至少 
\begin_inset Formula $(n-1)$
\end_inset

 阶可导的函数 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ u_{i}\right\} _{i=1}^{n}$
\end_inset

，若它们的 Wronskian 不恒为零，则它们线性独立；否则，它们线性相关。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
关于 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ k_{i}\right\} _{i=1}^{n}$
\end_inset

 的线性代数方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{bmatrix}\begin{array}{llll}
u_{1} & u_{2} & \cdots & u_{n}\\
u_{1}' & u_{2}' & \cdots & u_{n}'\\
\cdots & \cdots & \cdots & \cdots\\
u_{1}^{(n-1)} & u_{2}^{(n-1)} & \cdots & u_{n}^{(n-1)}
\end{array}\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}k_{1}\\
k_{2}\\
\cdots\\
k_{n}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}0\\
0\\
\cdots\\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\]

\end_inset

有非零解，当且仅当系数矩阵的行列式为零。
